texts.FTUE_TEXT_SCHOOL_1: Congratulations! You have been accepted to Chef Panda's Pastry School!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_SCHOOL_2: Master these skills and you will become a Chef too!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_SCHOOL_3: Use this airship to navigate on your adventures!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_SCHOOL_4: Now go travel the world and learn new recipes!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_1_0:
Swap pieces to create matches
with 3 or more of the same color!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_2_0:
Match 4 of a kind
to make a Line Breaker!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_2_1:
Match with the Line Breaker
to use it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_3_0: Create an L-Shaped Match to build an Ice Cream Bomb!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_3_1: Match with the Ice Cream Bomb to use it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_4_0:
Make a T-Shaped Match
to build an X-Breaker!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_4_1:
Match with the X-Breaker
to use it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_5_0:
Make a Square-Shaped Match
to build a Bee!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_5_1: Bees will always seek out important pieces. Match with the Bee to use it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_6_0:
Match 5 of a kind
to build a Rainbow Cake!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_6_1:
Swap the Rainbow Cake
with any color to clear
that color from the board!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_0_6_2:
Great job! Reveal all the
Yumsicles to win!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_1_1_0:
Help Scoops to the end of the path by matching with special 
Energy pieces!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_2_1_0:
Don't forget to make
Square-Shaped Matches to get
help from the Bees!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_3_1_0: The Spoon breaks a single piece on the board. Tap it to use!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_3_2_0: Now tap this piece to crunch it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_3_3_0:
If you run out of Spoons
you can always get more!
Just tap the Spoon icon!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_4_1_0: Make matches to clear the Ice and Reveal the Yumsicles!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_5_1_0: Keep an eye out for Rocket Yumsicles on the board! When revealed they launch in the direction they are facing!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_6_1_0: Match over Waffles to collect them!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_8_1_0: Make a match next to Chocolate to break it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_9_1_0: Scoops will break through obstacles in their way!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_10_1_0: You unlocked the +5 Moves Booster! Click the icon to add 5 moves to this level.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_11_1_0:
Yummy Worms can only travel
under ice! Fully reveal a
Yummy Worm to collect it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_11_2_0: Match over a Yummy Worm's body and it will wiggle away!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_11_3_0: Reveal a Yummy Worm to collect it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_12_1_0: If there's nowhere a Yummy Worm can wiggle away to, matching next to a Yummy Worm's head will cause it to shake off a piece of ice!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_12_2_0: Match next to a Yummy Worm's head and it will wiggle away!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_13_1_0: If you need help with a level, click the hints button for tips!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_14_1_0: A Rolling Pin clears a whole row of pieces! Tap it to use!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_14_2_0: Now tap this row to clear it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_14_3_0: If you run out of Rolling Pins you can always get more! Just tap the Rolling Pin icon!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_16_1_0: Chocolate can have multiple layers. Break each layer to remove Chocolate!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_17_1_0:
Topplers can only run across
Graham Crackers. Help a Toppler
to the ground to collect it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_17_2_0:
Match near a Toppler
and watch them move!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_17_3_0:
Topplers will move toward the
tallest stack of 
Graham Crackers.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_17_4_0:
Match again to help
 the Toppler down!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_17_5_0: Now that the Toppler is off the Graham Cracker, make a match nearby to collect it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_17_6_0:
Great job! Now collect
the other Topplers!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_17_7_NG: Match near a Toppler to help them to the ground!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_17_8_NG: Match again to collect the Toppler!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_18_1_0: A Pastry Bag clears a whole column of pieces! Tap it to use!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_18_2_0:
Now tap any column to 
wipe it out!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_18_3_0: If you run out of Pastry Bags you can always get more! Just tap the Pastry Bag icon!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_20_1_0: You unlocked the Bomb Booster! Click the icon to add an Ice Cream Bomb to this level.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_STARCHEST_1: Earn stars to open the Star Bag for fantastic rewards!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_STARCHEST_2: You earned a Star Bag!  Let's open it now!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_01_1: You're doing a great job! Let's go to the Kitchen and make some tasty treats!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_01_2: Chef Panda needs your help to make some delicious Chocolate Chip Cookies!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_01_3: You already have the ingredients! Click this button to bake the cookies.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_01_4: Click the Make button to create this recipe.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_01_5: Recipes take time to bake. Click here to speed them up!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_01_6: Your recipe is done! Click here to claim it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_01_7: Great job ranking up! Keep baking recipes to earn more rewards!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_02_1: Hey Chef! You've been doing great! There's more I want to show you in the Kitchen!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_02_2: You can see all the recipes you have created by clicking the Display Case.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_02_3: Look at all these tasty recipes!  Click an item to learn more about it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_02_4: Here you can see your recipe's details. When you make this recipe multiple times, you will rank up its Mastery.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_02_5: Return to the Kitchen to make more recipes and fill out your Display Case!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_03_1: You earned a Star Bag!  Click here to redeem it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_03_2: Open your Star Bag to get fresh ingredients!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_03_3: Great job! Use your fresh ingredients to create yummy treats!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_04_1: Greetings, Chef!  I want to tell you about Display Case Collections!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_04_2: Let's go to the Display Case.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_04_3: By baking all the recipes in a Collection, you can unlock an Airship.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_04_4: Complete both recipes in the Sweet Collection to earn the Sweetberry Blimp!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_05_1: Salutations, Chef! I want to show you how to bake anything your heart desires!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_05_2: Let's go to the Display Case.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_05_3: You can bake anything available in your Display Case at any time! This can help you progress toward Recipe Mastery or completing a Collection. Let's go to the Vanilla Collection!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_05_4: I've given you the ingredients to make a Chocolate Roll Cake, make it whenever you want!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_CRAFTING_05_5: To make the Chocolate Roll Cake, click on it in your Display Case to bring up the recipe details. Then, click the Make button. You will return to the Kitchen and can begin making your delicious treat!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_SPINNER_01_1: You unlocked the Daily Spinner! Spin every day to win free prizes!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_21_1_0: Match near Donuts to remove them!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_22_1_0: The Oven Mitt lets you swap any two pieces on the board. It can also be used to move Topplers! Tap here to use it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_22_2_0:
Tap the first piece you 
want to swap.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_22_3_0: Now tap another piece to complete the swap!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_22_4_0: If you run out of Oven Mitts you can always get more! Just tap the Oven Mitt icon!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_25_1_0: Waffles can have multiple layers! Break each layer to remove the Waffles!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_26_1_0: Chocolate now has 3 layers! Make multiple matches next to it to break it!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_27_1_0: Look for Bombsicles on the board. They explode when you reveal them!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_30_1_0: You unlocked the Rainbow Cake Booster! Click the icon to add a Rainbow Cake to this level.
texts.FTUE_TEXT_31_1_0: Liquid makes the pieces float up!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_34_1_0: Friends have sent you Buddy Bees! Click here to use them!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_34_2_0: Now click on a piece to use the Buddy Bee!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_34_3_0: If you are connected to Facebook, you can receive Buddy Bees from your friends! Tap the Bee icon on the map screen to learn more!
texts.FTUE_TEXT_34_3_0_WEB: You can receive Buddy Bees from your friends! Tap the Bee icon on the map screen to learn more!

texts.FTUE_TEXT_101_8_0: Collect all the Hopplers to win!

texts.HINT_TEXT_04_009_01: A Conveyor Belt moves all objects on it every turn.
texts.HINT_TEXT_04_009_02: A Conveyor Belt can exit the board and return pieces elsewhere.

texts.HINT_TEXT_04_014_03: Break the Honey to use the pieces it has covered!
